"""Map background tiles (b492): 96x96 WebP room tiles keyed by CSS class.

Sliced from sprite_package/source_sheets/room_tiles_sheet.png. All 16
floor masks (open neighbours: N=1 E=2 S=4 W=8) are composited from ONE
visual family: eligible bases are every family tile/rotation whose
openings are a superset of the target mask; extras get sealed with
closed-wall bands from the family corridor tile. 4 variants per mask
(different bases incl. mossy decorated ones + lighting jitter) fight
repetition; a gamma/contrast/saturation lift keeps stone texture
readable at 42px on dark screens. Themed tiles share the same
normalization and enhancement. Every image is exactly 96x96.

Generated by scratchpad build script -- regenerate rather than edit.
"""

